# Vendored third-party checkouts. Cloned on demand by scripts/lib/deps.sh
# from deps/deps.list — see CLAUDE.md "Vendored deps".
#
# Anything dropped into deps/ is gitignored by default; the only tracked
# entries are this file and the explicit allowlist below.
*
!.gitignore
!deps.list
!libhybris-shims/
!libhybris-shims/**
!xwayland-patches/
!xwayland-patches/**
!mesa-patches/
!mesa-patches/**
